{"type":"text","timestamp":1775862897802,"sessionID":"ses_286572f10ffeSFQ2dtrLqZNTfc","part":{"id":"prt_d79ad3ba8001Y0JQdKgl3unBAG","messageID":"msg_d79ad213d001Bo2cmU3ILyf4Pz","sessionID":"ses_286572f10ffeSFQ2dtrLqZNTfc","type":"text","text":"All tests pass. Let me provide a summary of the AR-016 PicoD File Management API implementation:\n\n## Summary\n\nThe PicoD File Management API (`pkg/picod`) is fully implemented with:\n\n### Core Files\n- **`server.go`** - HTTP server with Gin engine, route registration\n- **`files.go`** - File upload (multipart/JSON), list, download handlers\n- **`auth.go`** - RS256 JWT authentication middleware\n- **`sanitize.go`** - Path sanitization for workspace jail security\n- **`execute.go`** - Command execution (from AR-015)\n- **`health.go`** - Health check endpoint\n- **`config.go`** - Server configuration\n- **`picod_test.go`** - 52 unit tests with 82.1% coverage\n\n### API Endpoints\n| Endpoint | Method | Auth | Handler |\n|----------|--------|------|---------|\n| `/health` | GET | No | HealthCheckHandler |\n| `/api/files` | POST | JWT | UploadFileHandler |\n| `/api/files` | GET | JWT | ListFilesHandler |\n| `/api/files/*path` | GET | JWT | DownloadFileHandler |\n\n### Security Features\n- Path traversal prevention via `sanitizePath`\n- Symlink resolution with workspace boundary check\n- JWT RS256 authentication with expiration validation\n- File mode limit (max 0777) to prevent setuid/setgid\n\n### Test Coverage\n- 82.1% statement coverage (exceeds 80% requirement)\n- Race detector passed\n- All 52 tests pass including:\n  - Multipart missing path/file\n  - Empty directory listing\n  - MIME type detection (JSON, unknown)\n  - Symlink inside workspace\n  - Full file lifecycle\n  - Large file upload (30 MiB)\n  - Concurrent operations","time":{"start":1775862897801,"end":1775862897801}}}
